snippet.title: 007 LEGENDS SKYFALL TRAILER
snippet.description: SKYFALL has arrived... and the game's final mission -- based on the blockbuster film in theaters now -- is available in the U.S. to download for free today on PlayStation Network, and November 20th on Xbox LIVE and Steam (PC).
